title: SALOME WHERE SHE DANCED Yvonne De Carlo, Rod Cameron, David Bruce

sources.title: SALOME WHERE SHE DANCED Yvonne De Carlo, Rod Cameron, David Bruce
sources.description: Anna Marie (Yvonne De Carlo) is a graceful Viennese ballerina as known as "Salome." After a prince she loved is killed in the Franco-Prussian war, she falls for an American journalist (Rod Cameron), who leads her into the treacherous world of espionage. When she makes her way to the Wild West, Salom e becomes involved with an outlaw named Cleve (David Bruce), whom she tries to reform. Then, to help her theater career, she befriends a Russian diplomat (Walter Slezak), making Cleve jealous.
